Kraft a Finalist: A work by Los Angeles composer William Kraft, 66, has been 
chosen for the final round in the competition for the Kennedy Center Friedheim 
Awards, and will be played on a concert of four competing works by American 
composers at the Washington, D.C., center on Oct. 28. Announced Wednesday, the 
