<HEADLINE>
<P>
PAKISTAN BOMBINGS KILL 10 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, Pakistan 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
At least 10 people were killed and more than 30 were injured in three bomb 
blasts Thursday in Pakistan's Punjab province, the official APP news agency 
said. 
</P>
<P>
There was no immediate information on who planted the bombs. 
</P>
