(CALIFORNIA); LOS ANGELES COUNTY SANITATION DISTRICTS; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS 
-- 1990; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS -- FINANCES; POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; POLITICAL 
