Jr.; Kevin Gilliam, RB, 5-8, 175, Sr.; Nicky Levale, RB, 5-11, 216, So.; Scott 
McGarrh, WR, 5-11, Jr.; Dang Nguyen, LB, 5-10, 165, Sr.; Joe Polman, LB, 6-2, 
211, Sr.; Noa Utu, LB, 6-2, 212, Sr. 
