</P>
<P>
Outlook: In his first year at as Santiago coach, Allen, an assistant coach at 
Whittier College the past three years, is trying to revitalize a team that 
hasn't finished higher than fifth the last two seasons. To do so, he'll have to 
depend on all-league linebackers Polman and Utu, both of who are on major 
college material because of their size and speed, to solidify a defensive unit. 
</P>
