<HEADLINE>
<P>
ROCKWELL INTERNATIONAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Rockwell International Corp. in Seal Beach won a $7-million contract to 
research a space-based laser-ground-based laser, concept formulation and 
technology development planning program. 
</P>
