<P>
Civil lawsuit -- An article Aug. 12 incorrectly reported that The Wellington 
Group had been barred from conducting business or occupying its Torrance 
offices as a result of a civil lawsuit brought against the company by the state 
Department of Corporations. In fact, Wellington has remained open, though it 
was barred by the court from selling securities. 
</P>
